WEBVTT

00:06.407 --> 00:08.276
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:08.309 --> 00:10.111
MY PARTNER IS DEAD.

00:10.144 --> 00:12.913
I'M GONNA GET THIS GUY,
AND I'M GONNA KILL HIM.

00:12.947 --> 00:14.415
HE WAS MY PARTNER.

00:14.448 --> 00:15.249
Andy:
OH, HOLY SHIT.

00:15.283 --> 00:16.751
THE TIJUANA POLICE?

00:16.784 --> 00:17.885
DON'T ENJOY THIS.

00:17.918 --> 00:20.221
WE SHOULD FLEE.
AND I LOVE YOU.

00:20.254 --> 00:22.123
I NEED YOU TO TAKE SHANE
UP TO MY SISTER'S.

00:22.156 --> 00:24.558
Shane:
SHE BANGED UNCLE ANDY.
Asshole!

00:24.592 --> 00:26.560
DO NOT
MAKE ME GO BACK THERE.

00:26.594 --> 00:28.296
EVERYONE HATES ME.

00:28.329 --> 00:29.664
WHERE IN THE FUCK AM I?

00:29.697 --> 00:31.165
Man:
YOU'RE IN TEXAS, MA'AM.

00:31.198 --> 00:32.266
MR. SANDUSKY.

00:32.300 --> 00:34.068
I NEED SOME POT.

00:34.101 --> 00:36.237
I WANT TO OPEN A STORE ‐‐
MEDICAL MARIJUANA.

00:36.270 --> 00:37.438
DOUG IS HELPING ME.

00:37.471 --> 00:39.006
WE CAN'T APPROVE
YOUR APPLICATION
WITHOUT THE CONSENT

00:39.040 --> 00:40.374
OF A LOCAL
LAW‐ENFORCEMENT OFFICIAL.

00:40.408 --> 00:42.276
YOU GUYS
WANT TO SELL DRUGS?

00:42.310 --> 00:43.244
I'M GONNA WANT MY CUT.

00:43.277 --> 00:45.846
YOU WILL LIE BACK
AND SHOW THERE IS A BABY

00:45.880 --> 00:47.248
THAT IS BOTH MALE
AND MINE.

00:47.281 --> 00:50.117
YOU REMEMBER SUCIO.
HE WILL WATCH YOU NOW.

00:50.151 --> 00:51.919
WHERE IS SUCIO?
Nancy:
THERE WAS BLOOD.

00:51.953 --> 00:53.621
GET YOURSELF
TO A SAFE PLACE.

00:53.654 --> 00:54.755
Wait for my call.

01:11.272 --> 01:13.975
[ <i>GUNSHOTS</i>]

01:14.008 --> 01:16.744
[ SIGHS ]
WHAT ARE WE DOING HERE, NANCE?

01:16.777 --> 01:18.946
BIG BUFFALO BLASTING.

01:18.980 --> 01:20.114
SAYS SO
RIGHT ON THE THING.

01:20.147 --> 01:22.416
NO, HERE,
FAMILY FUN BOWL‐O‐RAMA.

01:22.450 --> 01:25.353
I'M OUT OF TOKENS.
I BOWLED SEVEN FULL GAMES.

01:25.386 --> 01:28.389
I'M BEING RECRUITED
FOR LEAGUE, SO THAT ‐‐

01:28.422 --> 01:29.657
I WANT TO GO HOME.

01:29.690 --> 01:31.392
[ <i>GUNSHOT, BOING!</i>]

01:31.425 --> 01:32.460
YOU SHOT A BUNNY.

01:32.493 --> 01:35.029
DON'T THINK YOU'RE SUPPOSED
TO BLAST THE BUNNY.

01:35.062 --> 01:36.864
[ HOOTING]
OR THE OWL.

01:36.897 --> 01:39.934
WHEN ESTEBAN CALLS,
WE CAN ALL GO HOME.

01:39.967 --> 01:43.704
THEN YOU'LL BE FREE TO SIT
YOUR SISTER‐FUCKING ASS

01:43.738 --> 01:45.373
DOWN ON THE COUCH,

01:45.406 --> 01:46.340
GET HIGH,

01:46.374 --> 01:49.076
SCHEDULE YOUR
POST‐SISTER‐FUCKING JERK SESSION

01:49.110 --> 01:51.245
WHEREIN YOU RELIVE
ALL THE MANY PLEASURES

01:51.279 --> 01:53.180
OF FUCKING MY SISTER.

01:54.615 --> 01:56.817
UH‐HUH. YEAH.

01:56.851 --> 01:59.287
I SEE
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE.

01:59.987 --> 02:01.255
DON'T.

02:01.289 --> 02:02.323
WHAT?

02:02.356 --> 02:03.391
JUST DON'T.

02:03.424 --> 02:05.393
FINE.
YOU'RE JEALOUS.

02:05.426 --> 02:07.595
YOU'RE PISSED ABOUT JILL.
I JUST SAID
I DIDN'T WANT TO DO THIS.

02:07.628 --> 02:09.630
YOU DON'T NEED TO WAIT
FOR ESTEBAN TO CALL.
I REALLY DON'T WANT TO GET
INTO YOUR WHOLE ‐‐

02:09.664 --> 02:11.198
ERGO...
ERGO.
ERGO...

02:11.232 --> 02:12.433
ERGO ‐‐ REALLY?!
IT'S NOT ABOUT ‐‐
IT'S ABOUT ME.

02:12.466 --> 02:14.168
IT IS SO NOT ABOUT YOU.
THAT NIGHT IN THE CAR!

02:14.201 --> 02:16.304
THAT WAS FOR THE COPS,
ANDY.
THE PASSION ‐‐
AT BORDER FENCE.

02:16.337 --> 02:18.639
PASSION? I WAS TRYING
NOT TO PEE IN MY PANTS.
YOU FELT SOMETHING.

02:18.673 --> 02:19.640
ENOUGH.
ENOUGH.

02:19.674 --> 02:20.741
YOU ‐‐ YOU TRY TO HIDE
YOUR FEELINGS.

02:20.775 --> 02:22.410
THIS IS BULLSHIT.
BULLSHIT.

02:22.443 --> 02:23.244
BULLSHIT.
BULLSHIT. HUH.

02:23.277 --> 02:24.779
OKAY, SO KISS ME.

02:27.748 --> 02:29.350
GO AWAY.

02:31.085 --> 02:32.653
You like me.

02:32.687 --> 02:33.854
YOU LIKE ME LIKE ME,

02:33.888 --> 02:36.090
AND THAT'S WHY
YOU DON'T WANT TO.

02:36.123 --> 02:38.626
BABY, ANDY.

02:38.659 --> 02:41.963
BABY, baby, baby, baby.

02:41.996 --> 02:44.165
ANOTHER MAN'S BABY.

02:47.101 --> 02:47.902
[ <i>GUNSHOT</i>]

02:47.935 --> 02:49.103
AND ANOTHER BUNNY.

02:49.136 --> 02:53.040
[ <i>GUNSHOTS, ANIMALS SCREAMING</i>]

02:53.074 --> 02:55.810
I'M HOPING SHE FALLS DOWN
A FLIGHT OF STAIRS.

02:55.843 --> 02:58.879
THIS THING IS HAPPENING
WHETHER WE LIKE IT OR NOT.

02:59.380 --> 03:00.181
SHIT!

03:00.214 --> 03:02.416
YOU DON'T WANT
A PINK BEAR ANYWAY.

03:02.450 --> 03:03.951
FUCK THE BEAR.
I WANT TO WIN.

03:03.985 --> 03:05.186
OKAY.
TIME TO GO.

03:05.219 --> 03:07.054
ESTEBAN'S MEETING US
AT THE HOUSE.

03:07.088 --> 03:08.990
SO WE DO GET
TO MEET BABY DADDY.

03:09.023 --> 03:11.225
BE NICE OR SAY NOTHING.

03:11.258 --> 03:13.427
[ CRICKETS CHIRPING ]

03:16.897 --> 03:18.132
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

03:18.165 --> 03:20.334
I'VE, UH,
BROUGHT YOU THIS.

03:22.103 --> 03:24.905
OH, THOSE ARE AWESOME SHIRTS.
I WISH YOU'D BROUGHT THREE.

03:24.939 --> 03:29.176
SO, YOU'RE THE MAYOR OF MEXICO
OR SOMETHING?

03:29.210 --> 03:31.345
OR...SOMETHING, YES.

03:31.379 --> 03:34.215
AND YOU STUCK YOUR PENIS
INSIDE MY MOTHER...

03:34.248 --> 03:35.182
AT LEAST ONCE.

03:35.216 --> 03:37.918
OKAY, THEN. GOODNIGHT, SHANE.
GO UPSTAIRS.

03:37.952 --> 03:39.220
NOW YOU'RE SURE
IT'S SAFE UP THERE?

03:39.253 --> 03:41.389
WHAT HAPPENED
TO THE SMELLY GUARD DOG?

03:41.422 --> 03:44.392
OH, CESAR BELIEVES HE MIXED UP
HIS MEDICATIONS

03:44.425 --> 03:45.993
AND, UM, WANDERED OFF.

03:46.027 --> 03:49.930
I MIXED, UH, BENADRYL
AND TEGRETOL ONE TIME,

03:49.964 --> 03:52.867
SPENT THREE DAYS GUESSING WEIGHT
AT THE IOWA STATE FAIR,

03:52.900 --> 03:55.403
GOT CRABS, AND A TATTOO...

03:55.436 --> 03:58.072
OF A CRAB.

03:58.105 --> 04:00.207
SO, HE JUST WANDERED OFF
NAKED AND BLEEDING?

04:00.241 --> 04:02.410
I AM TOLD
THAT'S HAPPENED BEFORE, YES.

04:02.443 --> 04:03.544
OH.

04:03.577 --> 04:04.946
WELL, IN THAT CASE,

04:04.979 --> 04:07.014
THANK YOU FOR GIVING HIM A GUN
AND THE KEYS TO OUR HOUSE.

04:07.048 --> 04:10.151
UH, HOW ABOUT MOVING
INTO MY HOUSE?

04:15.089 --> 04:17.291
DID YOU JUST ASK ME
TO LIVE WITH YOU?

04:17.325 --> 04:18.826
Andy:
IN TIJUANA?

04:18.859 --> 04:19.860
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:19.894 --> 04:21.228
EVEN THE DONKEYS
ARE SCARED,

04:21.262 --> 04:22.997
AND THAT'S A FUN PLACE
TO BE A DONKEY.

04:23.030 --> 04:25.299
I OWN A HOUSE HERE...

04:25.333 --> 04:26.400
IN SANTA PLAYA.

04:27.501 --> 04:28.970
THERE'S PLENTY OF ROOM ‐‐

04:29.003 --> 04:33.474
ROOM FOR THE BOYS
AND, UH, EVEN ROOM FOR <i>HIM.</i>

04:33.507 --> 04:36.177
I'M GOOD, ACTUALLY, HERE.

04:36.210 --> 04:37.111
ME TOO.

04:37.144 --> 04:40.247
I THINK...
IT WOULD BE BEST.

04:40.281 --> 04:42.350
YEAH, WELL,
YOU'RE NOT THE MAYOR OF US.

04:42.383 --> 04:44.352
AND THESE SHIRTS ARE LAME!

04:45.386 --> 04:47.188
SHANE, GO TO BED <i>NOW.</i>

04:47.221 --> 04:49.857
COME ON, TOUGH GUY.

04:51.692 --> 04:53.394
NICE TO MEET YOU.

04:53.427 --> 04:57.898
[ FOOTSTEPS ]

04:59.667 --> 05:02.903
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

05:04.105 --> 05:06.307
YOU DIDN'T ANSWER
MY QUESTION.

05:06.340 --> 05:07.842
THIS IS OUR HOME.

05:07.875 --> 05:10.411
AND WHERE IS OUR HOME?

05:10.444 --> 05:13.047
WHERE IS THIS
COMING FROM?

05:14.448 --> 05:17.818
I RECEIVED
THE TEST RESULTS.

05:17.852 --> 05:21.455
IT IS INDEED A BOY.
MY BOY.

05:21.489 --> 05:24.558
OH. I SEE.

05:24.592 --> 05:26.260
YOUR BOY.

05:27.461 --> 05:29.297
[ CHUCKLES ]

05:29.330 --> 05:31.532
OH, GOD, LOOK AT THE TIME!

05:31.565 --> 05:34.602
WE SHOULD GO TO BED, NANCE,
LET THIS POOR GUY LEAVE.

05:34.635 --> 05:37.338
UH, IGNACIO!

05:37.371 --> 05:38.873
ANOTHER GUARD DOG.

05:38.906 --> 05:40.908
IGNACIO WILL WATCH OVER YOU
FOR NOW.

05:40.942 --> 05:42.977
YOU KNOW WHAT?
I CAN DO THE WATCHING.

05:43.010 --> 05:44.145
I'M AN EXCELLENT WATCHER.

05:44.178 --> 05:47.048
[ CHUCKLES ] RIGHT.
YOU AND YOUR CRABS.

05:47.081 --> 05:49.116
[ CHUCKLES ]

05:50.718 --> 05:52.153
THIS IS FOR YOU, NANCY.

05:52.186 --> 05:56.090
"NOW AND ZEN
BABY CRADLE AND SWING"?

05:56.123 --> 05:57.825
IT'S A LITTLE EARLY,
DON'T YOU THINK?

05:57.858 --> 05:59.126
I'M NOT EVEN SHOWING.

06:02.296 --> 06:04.532
I CAN FEEL HIM.

06:05.800 --> 06:08.202
[ SMOOCHES ]

06:08.235 --> 06:12.206
LOOK AT THIS GUY.
HE'S A GORILLA.

06:12.239 --> 06:13.441
HE'S A THUG!

06:13.474 --> 06:15.943
I MEAN,
TAKE AWAY THE [LAUGHS]

06:15.977 --> 06:17.979
THE MUSCLES
AND THE FIERY EYES

06:18.012 --> 06:20.114
AND THE COLD HEART
OF A KILLER,

06:20.147 --> 06:22.817
WHAT DOES HE HAVE
THAT I DON'T HAVE?

06:22.850 --> 06:25.086
AAH!
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLING ]

06:25.119 --> 06:27.822
I CALL HIM MR. ZAPPY.
[ CRACKLES ]

06:27.855 --> 06:30.491
OH, GREAT.
NOW HE'S WET HIMSELF.

06:30.524 --> 06:32.259
[ CHUCKLES ]
THAT HAPPENS.

06:32.293 --> 06:34.829
I'LL GET HIM A TOWEL.

06:34.862 --> 06:37.531
YOU'RE GONNA LOVE
THIS SWING.

06:37.565 --> 06:40.201
ONLY THE BEST
FOR OUR BOY.

06:40.234 --> 06:41.736
"Our boy."

06:41.769 --> 06:43.304
MM‐HMM.

06:44.772 --> 06:48.376
"NOTHING IS EXACTLY
AS IT SEEMS,

06:48.409 --> 06:51.279
NOR IS IT OTHERWISE."

06:51.312 --> 06:52.380
WHAT?

06:52.413 --> 06:55.449
It says so
right on the box.

06:55.483 --> 06:58.286
[ GRUNTS SOFTLY ]

07:00.087 --> 07:04.158
SMOKING IN THE ECO‐GARDEN.
WAY TO RAISE THE BAR.

07:04.191 --> 07:05.993
I NEED TO TOP OFF
MY FEED BAG.

07:06.027 --> 07:08.296
HOW MUCH MORE JOLLY GREEN
CAN YOU GET ME?

07:08.329 --> 07:09.463
HOW MUCH CAN YOU SPEND?

07:09.497 --> 07:10.765
FOUR GRAND.

07:10.798 --> 07:12.633
YOU HAVE FOUR EXTRA GRAND?

07:12.667 --> 07:15.503
UNIONS REALLY ARE RUINING
THIS COUNTRY.

07:15.536 --> 07:17.204
[ SCHOOL BELL RINGING ]

07:17.238 --> 07:19.540
I GOT "CHOOSING CHASTITY"
IN THE SCIENCE ROOM TILL 5:00.

07:19.573 --> 07:21.008
SO I'LL MEET YOU AFTER.

07:21.042 --> 07:24.645
THAT "ABSTINENCE ONLY" BULLSHIT?
BLOW IT OFF.

07:24.679 --> 07:26.047
CAN'T.

07:26.080 --> 07:27.682
IF I SPLIT
BEFORE THE MOVIE ENDS,

07:27.715 --> 07:30.384
THE HAMSTERS GET RAPED
WITH SHARPIES.

07:30.418 --> 07:32.386
[ <i>CAT MEOWING, DOG BARKING</i>]

07:32.420 --> 07:35.222
AH, THE NESTING PHASE.

07:35.256 --> 07:39.026
HEY, AM I RACE‐BIASED,
OR THIS A NEW MEXICAN BODYGUARD?

07:39.060 --> 07:40.094
BRAND‐NEW.

07:40.127 --> 07:41.829
HI. HOLA.

07:41.862 --> 07:43.197
[ <i>BARKING, MEOWING CONTINUE</i>]

07:43.230 --> 07:46.400
THE CAT IS MILO.
THE DOG IS OTIS.

07:46.434 --> 07:49.337
THE CAT IS CRAZY,
AND THE LITTLE DOG JUST FOLLOWS!

07:49.370 --> 07:50.338
[ LAUGHS ]

07:50.371 --> 07:51.372
RIGHT.

07:52.573 --> 07:54.342
SO, I'M GONNA GO NOW.

07:54.375 --> 07:55.743
GOOD LUCK.

07:55.776 --> 07:57.144
OH, HAVE YOU SEEN ANDY?

07:57.178 --> 08:01.682
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]
HE'S IN THE GARAGE WORKING OUT.

08:01.716 --> 08:04.986
Ignacio:
JUMP, LITTLE DOG, JUMP!

08:06.988 --> 08:09.223
HEY,
JUST IN TIME TO SPOT ME.

08:09.256 --> 08:12.193
IS THIS 'CAUSE YOU
PISSED YOURSELF LAST NIGHT?

08:12.226 --> 08:14.495
NO. YES.

08:14.528 --> 08:15.763
ANYWAY, HE CHEATED.

08:15.796 --> 08:19.667
I COULD USE YOUR HELP
WITH MY ZEN BABY ERECTOR KIT.

08:19.700 --> 08:22.370
[ GRUNTS, PANTING ]

08:22.403 --> 08:25.206
BIG SHOWDOWN COMING,
NANCE.

08:25.239 --> 08:27.308
HIGH NOON.

08:27.341 --> 08:29.143
I CAN FEEL IT IN MY BONES.

08:30.978 --> 08:33.180
WHERE'D YOU GET
THE BOX O' PAIN?

08:34.081 --> 08:36.083
WHAT?
THIS IS MY STUFF.

08:36.117 --> 08:38.586
IT'S MY, UH,
ATHLETE STUFF.

08:38.619 --> 08:41.289
IT'S JUDAH'S.
HE WAS GOOD AT SPORTS.

08:41.322 --> 08:42.490
I WAS GOOD AT FLEEING.

08:42.523 --> 08:43.891
[ CHUCKLES ]

08:43.924 --> 08:45.793
YOU KNOW,
I HAVE A BODYGUARD.

08:45.826 --> 08:48.729
I DON'T NEED YOU TO CRUSH
MY FOES IN YOUR ARMPIT.

08:48.763 --> 08:51.165
YEAH?

08:51.198 --> 08:53.367
WELL,
WHAT DO YOU NEED FROM ME?

08:55.670 --> 08:58.072
THE DOORBELL IS BARKING.

08:58.105 --> 09:02.376
YOU LOOK LIKE, UH,
JAMIE LEE CURTIS IN "PERFECT."

09:02.410 --> 09:07.014
YOU DO, KINDA.
[ LAUGHING ]

09:09.116 --> 09:11.485
OH, GOOD.
JUST SO YOU KNOW...

09:11.519 --> 09:13.154
THAT'S WHAT
I WAS GOING FOR.

09:24.532 --> 09:26.033
CELIA.

09:26.067 --> 09:27.101
[ SIGHS ]

09:27.134 --> 09:27.902
NANCY.

09:27.935 --> 09:29.604
WHAT A WONDERFUL SURPRISE.

09:29.637 --> 09:31.405
REALLY?

09:31.439 --> 09:32.139
NO.

09:32.173 --> 09:35.443
NOT WONDERFUL,
NOT A SURPRISE.

09:35.476 --> 09:37.144
YOU WANT TO COME IN?

09:37.178 --> 09:39.447
THANK YOU.

09:39.480 --> 09:41.816
OH. IT'S <i>YOU.</i>

09:41.849 --> 09:44.318
YOU, YOU, YOU.

09:49.557 --> 09:51.325
IT'S COMPLICATED.

09:51.359 --> 09:53.294
IS THAT A SUITCASE?

09:53.327 --> 09:55.663
YES, IT IS.

09:55.696 --> 09:58.366
NO. YOU CAN'T STAY HERE.
LISTEN, NANCY,
I'VE BEEN THINKING.

09:58.399 --> 10:00.334
YOU CAN'T STAY HERE!
YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHAT I WAS GONNA SAY!

10:00.368 --> 10:01.569
YOU CAN'T STAY HERE!

10:01.602 --> 10:03.037
I WAS KIDNAPPED.

10:03.070 --> 10:06.140
YES, THANK YOU SO MUCH
FOR THE RANSOM.

10:06.173 --> 10:09.944
THEY WERE GONNA SELL MY
GALL BLADDER TO THE JAPANESE.

10:09.977 --> 10:13.814
FORTUNATELY,
MY BODY IS A TOXIC PIT.

10:15.383 --> 10:17.551
[ SIGHS ]
AND I ESCAPED...

10:17.585 --> 10:18.786
HEROICALLY.

10:18.819 --> 10:20.521
AND NOW I AM HOMELESS.

10:20.554 --> 10:23.524
[ SIGHS ]
CELIA...

10:23.557 --> 10:25.293
I'M PREGNANT.

10:26.327 --> 10:27.295
WITH A BABY?

10:27.328 --> 10:28.796
YES, WITH A BABY.

10:28.829 --> 10:32.366
WHICH MEANS I NEED QUIET...

10:32.400 --> 10:34.402
AND CALM AND ‐‐

10:34.435 --> 10:35.937
THANK YOU ‐‐

10:35.970 --> 10:38.773
AND HAPPY THOUGHTS AROUND ME
AS MUCH AS POSSIBLE.

10:38.806 --> 10:42.810
AND YOU, CELIA,
ARE NOT QUIET, NOT CALM.

10:42.843 --> 10:45.613
YOU ARE SO TERRIBLY, MISERABLY,
THOROUGHLY UNHAPPY

10:45.646 --> 10:47.448
THAT IF I PRICKED
YOUR FINGER,

10:47.481 --> 10:50.151
YOU'D BLEED A FUCKING
RAIN CLOUD!

10:50.184 --> 10:51.619
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

10:51.652 --> 10:54.055
IS IT ANDY'S?

10:54.088 --> 10:56.490
COME ON.

11:00.294 --> 11:01.896
COME ON.

11:14.609 --> 11:18.613
NOBODY PUTS BABY IN THE CORNER.

11:18.646 --> 11:22.283
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

11:23.918 --> 11:27.989
OH, THIS PLACE PERFECT
FOR ANY BUSINESS!

11:28.022 --> 11:30.358
THERE'S PLENTY OF ROOM.

11:30.391 --> 11:32.126
LOCATION'S GREAT.

11:32.159 --> 11:33.728
NOT SO EAGER.

11:33.761 --> 11:36.731
YOU REALLY GOT TO JEW
THESE SLOPES DOWN.

11:36.764 --> 11:38.733
PLEASE DON'T DO THAT.

11:38.766 --> 11:41.802
YOU WANT THE FISH?
BUY THE FISH.

11:41.836 --> 11:43.871
DON'T SQUEEZE THE FISH!

11:43.904 --> 11:45.906
I'M NOT SQUEEZING THE FISH.
I'M SNIFFING IT.

11:45.940 --> 11:47.808
AND I HAVE EVERY RIGHT
TO SNIFF THE FISH

11:47.842 --> 11:49.477
IF I'M GONNA BUY IT ‐‐
OR RENT IT.

11:49.510 --> 11:50.911
WE'LL TAKE IT.
[ CHUCKLES ]

11:50.945 --> 11:52.847
WHAT KIND OF BUSINESS
YOU GOT, ANYWAY?

11:52.880 --> 11:55.783
IT'S A
COMPASSIONATE CARE CLUB.

11:55.816 --> 11:58.386
OOH!
THAT GYM FOR FAT LADIES?

11:58.419 --> 12:00.988
MEDICAL MARIJUANA,
ACTUALLY.

12:01.022 --> 12:04.091
OH, NO.
NO, NO, NO!

12:04.125 --> 12:07.495
YOU SELL POT IN HERE,
FEDS TAKE AWAY MY BUILDING!

12:07.528 --> 12:09.830
YEAH, WELL,
YOU EAT DOGS.

12:09.864 --> 12:14.035
AH, GET THE FUCK OUT,
ASSWHORE!

12:16.203 --> 12:17.371
[ SIGHS ]

12:17.405 --> 12:22.276
"PUSH THE SEAT BACK TO DOWN
UNTIL IT SNAPS INTO PLACE."

12:23.544 --> 12:25.646
SNAP. SNAP. SNAP!

12:25.680 --> 12:27.915
PLASTIC DEMON FROM HELL!

12:27.949 --> 12:31.552
[ LULLABY PLAYS ]

12:31.585 --> 12:33.421
[ SIGHS ]

12:34.622 --> 12:36.157
MOMMY NEEDS TO GET DRUNK.

12:38.292 --> 12:39.593
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

12:39.627 --> 12:42.196
[ FOOTSTEPS ]

12:42.229 --> 12:44.298
[ IGNACIO GRUNTING ]

12:44.332 --> 12:48.169
[ LULLABY CONTINUES ]

12:51.706 --> 12:53.708
[ GRUNTING ]

12:53.741 --> 12:57.745
HE LOOK LITTLE, BUT HE'S HEAVIER
THAN A SEA TURTLE!

12:59.280 --> 13:02.583
[ BOTH PANTING ]

13:02.617 --> 13:04.652
WHAT WAS HE
DOING OUT THERE?

13:04.685 --> 13:06.754
LOOKING IN THE WINDOW.

13:06.787 --> 13:08.990
MAYBE WAITING TO COME
INTO THE HOUSE FOR <i>YOU.</i>

13:09.023 --> 13:10.891
WHAT WAS HE
GONNA ARREST ME FOR?

13:10.925 --> 13:13.361
NO ARREST. KCCK!

13:13.394 --> 13:15.262
PISTOLA.

13:17.531 --> 13:19.367
CUCHILLO.

13:21.135 --> 13:23.237
HA!

13:23.271 --> 13:25.439
PUÃ‘O DE HIERRO.

13:25.473 --> 13:27.575
SANGRE
DE UN HOMBRE MUERTO.

13:27.608 --> 13:29.343
THAT'S VERY UNSANITARY.

13:30.244 --> 13:31.345
[ CLANG ]

13:31.379 --> 13:33.080
NO BADGE.

13:34.415 --> 13:36.417
TODAY HE'S NO COP.

13:36.450 --> 13:38.819
TODAY HE'S RAMBO.

13:40.488 --> 13:41.589
WAKE UP.

13:41.622 --> 13:45.126
REMEMBER ME,
ANGRY LITTLE PRINCESA?

13:45.159 --> 13:47.561
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLING ]
[ LAUGHS ]

13:47.595 --> 13:48.829
HELP ME GET HIM
INTO THE BATHROOM.

13:48.863 --> 13:50.665
[ GRUNTING ]
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

13:50.698 --> 13:51.866
PUT HIM IN THE TUB.

13:51.899 --> 13:53.901
OH, 'CAUSE HE PEED
HIS PANTS, RIGHT?
YES.

13:53.934 --> 13:56.037
I'M GOING TO BURN HIS CLOTHES,
DRAIN HIS BLOOD,

13:56.070 --> 13:58.072
AND MELT HIS BONES
WITH ACID.

13:58.105 --> 13:59.040
OH, RIGHT.

13:59.073 --> 14:00.708
[ CHUCKLES ]
OHH. HELP ME.

14:00.741 --> 14:02.543
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLING ]
KA KA KA KA KA KA!

14:02.576 --> 14:04.712
[ THUD ]

14:04.745 --> 14:07.281
NOT IN MY TUB.

14:09.984 --> 14:11.786
WHAT'S THAT THING
SUPPOSED TO BE?

14:11.819 --> 14:13.120
DOMESTIC BLISS.

14:13.154 --> 14:15.756
LOOKS LIKE SOMEONE SHAT
A TILT‐A‐WHIRL.

14:15.790 --> 14:18.292
YOU'RE THE MORAL CENTER
OF THIS FAMILY.

14:18.326 --> 14:20.227
LET ME ASK YOU SOMETHING.

14:20.261 --> 14:23.531
IS IT OKAY TO IMPERSONATE
YOUR DEAD BROTHER

14:23.564 --> 14:25.433
AND PSEUDO‐STEAL
SOME MONEY

14:25.466 --> 14:27.034
IF YOU'RE GONNA USE
THE CASH

14:27.068 --> 14:29.303
FOR THE FAMILY'S
GREATER GOOD?

14:29.337 --> 14:32.006
HIS PASSPORT'S UPSTAIRS
IN MY SOCK DRAWER.

14:32.039 --> 14:34.542
IF I WERE YOU,
I'D WEAR A HAT OR SOMETHING.

14:34.575 --> 14:36.777
RESEMBLANCE
IS, UH, SORT OF THIN.

14:36.811 --> 14:40.047
AND THAT WOULD BE A THUMBS‐UP!
GOOD STUFF.

14:40.081 --> 14:43.050
WHATCHA DOING WITH ALL
THE SMOKEABLE PRODUCT THERE?

14:43.084 --> 14:45.319
SELLING IT
TO MY ENGLISH TEACHER.

14:45.353 --> 14:47.021
[ GROANS ]

14:47.054 --> 14:49.190
FOR THE FAMILY'S GREATER GOOD,
OF COURSE, RIGHT?

14:49.223 --> 14:52.760
THE FAMILY THAT TRIED TO SHIP
MY ASS TO OAKLAND?

14:52.793 --> 14:54.295
SURE. THINK THAT.

14:55.696 --> 14:58.699
DESPITE THE ENORMOUS
HYPOCRITICAL ELEPHANT

14:58.733 --> 14:59.734
IN THE ROOM,

14:59.767 --> 15:01.736
I FEEL COMPELLED
TO EXPRESS ALARM

15:01.769 --> 15:03.537
AND POTENTIALLY DISMAY...

15:03.571 --> 15:06.741
AND FEAR
THAT SILAS WILL KILL YOU...

15:06.774 --> 15:09.143
AND REGRET...

15:09.176 --> 15:13.347
THAT YOUR TRUE‐NORTH
MORAL COMPASS

15:13.381 --> 15:17.084
HAS, UH,
GONE ON THE FRITZ.

15:17.118 --> 15:20.087
WHAT CAN I SAY?
I'M A BOTWIN.

15:20.121 --> 15:23.224
WE'RE NOT RESPONSIBLE
FOR ANYTHING WE DO.

15:29.363 --> 15:30.665
I ORDER YOU TO RELEASE ME.

15:30.698 --> 15:31.966
I AM A FEDERAL AGENT,

15:31.999 --> 15:34.669
AND THIS MAN IS WANTED
BY THE U. S. GOVERNMENT.

15:34.702 --> 15:36.470
IF YOU UNTIE HIM,
HE'LL KILL ME.

15:36.504 --> 15:39.507
YOU HAVE NO BADGE, ROY.
YOU'RE OUT HERE ALL ON YOUR OWN.

15:39.540 --> 15:41.842
I'M UNDERCOVER.
[ SCOFFS ]

15:41.876 --> 15:43.477
WHAT DID YOU DO TO SUCIO?

15:43.511 --> 15:44.378
WHO?

15:44.412 --> 15:46.280
THE DIRTY MEXICAN.

15:46.314 --> 15:47.248
SORRY.

15:47.281 --> 15:49.283
NO. IT'S TRUE.
HE STINKS LIKE PIG SHIT.

15:49.317 --> 15:50.851
HE KILLED MY PARTNER.

15:50.885 --> 15:52.086
WERE YOU GONNA
HURT ME, TOO?

15:52.119 --> 15:54.855
HE'S GOING TO KILL YOU.
HE'S GOING TO KILL ME.

15:54.889 --> 15:57.158
HE'S A KILLER!
NOT ME. I'M NICE.

15:57.191 --> 16:00.561
UNTIE ME, I KILL HIM,
WE GO WATCH "MILO AND OTIS."

16:00.594 --> 16:02.530
NO ONE IS KILLING ANYONE.
STOP IT.

16:02.563 --> 16:04.699
STOP KICKING EACH OTHER,
OR I'M GONNA MAKE YOU
PEE YOUR PANTS AGAIN.

16:04.732 --> 16:06.534
WHOSE SIDE ARE YOU ON?!

16:06.567 --> 16:07.935
SHE'S ON MY SIDE!

16:07.969 --> 16:09.403
SHE MAKING BABY
WITH THE BOSS.

16:14.575 --> 16:17.945
WHAT'S IT LIKE
FUCKING A MONSTER?

16:17.979 --> 16:21.082
YOU WILL NOT SPEAK THAT WAY
IN FRONT OF MY CHILD!

16:21.115 --> 16:24.285
YOU CAN'T KEEP US HERE LIKE THIS
FOR LONG!

16:24.318 --> 16:25.620
WHO'S IT GONNA BE?

16:25.653 --> 16:26.787
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

16:26.821 --> 16:29.290
[ DOOR OPENS ]
Celia: HELLO, NANCY?

16:29.323 --> 16:30.524
YOU HOME?

16:30.558 --> 16:33.227
MAKE A SOUND,
I KILL YOU BOTH.

16:34.662 --> 16:39.467
[ GRUNTING ]

16:39.500 --> 16:42.336
HEY, HEY, HEY!
YOU GOT A BONER!

16:42.370 --> 16:45.940
IT'S A PERFECTLY NORMAL REACTION
TO THE ADRENALINE OF COMBAT!

16:45.973 --> 16:47.775
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.
THAT'S NOT COOL, MAN.

16:47.808 --> 16:49.310
[ GRUNTING ] NO.

16:49.343 --> 16:51.712
I DON'T WANT TO FIGHT NO MORE
WITH YOU!

16:51.746 --> 16:52.880
HI, NANCY.

16:52.913 --> 16:56.017
OKAY, WELL, THE DOOR WAS OPEN,
SO I JUST ‐‐

16:56.050 --> 16:59.854
WELL, NOT EXACTLY OPEN,
BUT AJAR.

16:59.887 --> 17:03.291
UH, MOSTLY,
IT WAS UNLOCKED.

17:03.324 --> 17:04.358
I'VE BEEN THINKING.

17:04.392 --> 17:08.429
I KNOW YOU SAID I COULDN'T
LIVE HERE, PER SE,

17:08.462 --> 17:10.131
IN THE HOUSE PROPER.

17:10.164 --> 17:12.266
BUT IT IS
SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA,

17:12.300 --> 17:15.202
AND YOU DO HAVE
THAT NICE SCREEN PORCH,

17:15.236 --> 17:16.203
BACK THERE,

17:16.237 --> 17:18.339
WITH THE...COUCH.

17:18.372 --> 17:21.809
SO ‐‐
HEY, THAT'S <i>FIRE.</i>

17:21.842 --> 17:24.378
OKAY, YOU KNOW,
TAKE IT EASY.

17:24.412 --> 17:27.214
TAKE IT EASY.
OW, NANCY! GOD!

17:27.248 --> 17:27.949
HANG ON A MINUTE.

17:27.982 --> 17:30.151
OKAY, FINAL NET,
EXTRA HOLD.

17:30.184 --> 17:33.587
THIS IS COTTON.
I AM HIGHLY FLAMMABLE RIGHT NOW.

17:33.621 --> 17:35.623
YOU KNOW WHAT?
YOU'RE CRAZY.

17:35.656 --> 17:39.327
YOU ARE FUCKING CRAZY,
AND I HATE YOU!

17:42.263 --> 17:43.364
WE'LL JUST TALK LATER.

17:52.139 --> 17:56.744
$186,437.96?

17:56.777 --> 17:58.412
THAT'S RIGHT,
MR. BOTWIN.

17:58.446 --> 18:00.214
JUDAH.
CALL ME JUDAH.

18:00.247 --> 18:02.984
WELL, JUDAH, I HAVEN'T SEEN
ONE OF THESE IN A LONG TIME.

18:03.017 --> 18:06.087
OH, YEAH, WELL, THAT LITTLE
COLLECTOR'S ITEM THERE ‐‐

18:06.120 --> 18:09.223
OH! ‐‐ WAS GIVEN
TO MY BROTHER AND ME.

18:09.256 --> 18:11.759
WE BOTH GOT ONE ‐‐
THIS ONE'S MINE, OBVIOUSLY ‐‐

18:11.792 --> 18:14.228
WHEN MY
GREAT UNCLE YITZHAK TRIPPED

18:14.261 --> 18:17.331
AND ACCIDENTALLY LOCKED HIMSELF
IN A FREEZER CHEST.

18:17.365 --> 18:18.499
INTERESTING SIDE NOTE ‐‐

18:18.532 --> 18:21.702
IT'S STILL THE ONLY CASE OF
HYPOTHERMIA IN WOODLAND HILLS.

18:21.736 --> 18:25.106
ANYWAY, IT WAS A LOT OF MONEY
FOR A YOUNG BOY.

18:25.139 --> 18:29.477
BUT I WAS SMART ENOUGH TO PUT IT
ASIDE FOR A RAINY DAY!

18:29.510 --> 18:30.845
UNLIKE MY STUPID BROTHER,

18:30.878 --> 18:32.913
WHO BLEW HIS
ON A '72 FORD ECONOLINE

18:32.947 --> 18:35.249
WHEN HE NEEDED A PLACE
TO LIVE ONE SUMMER.

18:35.283 --> 18:36.651
SO IT'S...

18:36.684 --> 18:39.453
GOD, I BET HE WISHES
HE DIDN'T DO THAT!

18:39.487 --> 18:42.423
[ Chuckling ]
ESPECIALLY WITH THE AMAZING
GROWTH ON THAT ACCOUNT.

18:42.456 --> 18:43.924
WHAT AN ASSHOLE.

18:43.958 --> 18:46.193
WELL, ACTUALLY,
THE GROWTH'S BEEN AVERAGE.

18:46.227 --> 18:49.664
YOU GRANDMOTHER HAS BEEN ADDING
TO IT FOR ALMOST 30 YEARS.

18:49.697 --> 18:51.365
THAT BITCH!

18:51.399 --> 18:52.633
I MEAN, IT SADDENS ME

18:52.667 --> 18:57.238
THAT SHE WOULD SO BLATANTLY
FAVOR ONE GRANDSON OVER ANOTHER.

18:57.271 --> 19:00.107
NOW, UM, ABOUT THE HOLD

19:00.141 --> 19:01.842
THAT YOU PUT
ON THIS ACCOUNT ‐‐

19:01.876 --> 19:04.345
LISTEN, I DON'T KNOW
WHAT SORT OF BULLSHIT

19:04.378 --> 19:05.413
HE'S TRYING TO PULL,

19:05.446 --> 19:08.015
BUT YOU TELL JUDAH
HE'S GONNA HAVE TO COME IN HERE

19:08.049 --> 19:11.118
AND TALK TO ME BEFORE HE'S GONNA
SEE DIME ONE OF THIS.

19:12.186 --> 19:14.221
I HAVE BEEN WAITING
A VERY, VERY LONG TIME

19:14.255 --> 19:16.424
TO SAY MY PIECE
TO JUDAH BOTWIN,

19:16.457 --> 19:18.359
AND BY GOD,
I'M GONNA SAY IT!

19:18.392 --> 19:20.261
NOW GET HIM IN HERE.

19:23.531 --> 19:25.199
UM...

19:25.232 --> 19:26.867
JUDAH DIED.

19:31.372 --> 19:34.308
HE'S ‐‐ HE'S DEAD.

19:39.447 --> 19:41.382
[ SOBBING ]

19:49.757 --> 19:52.293
[ SOBBING CONTINUES ]

19:52.326 --> 19:53.594
[ CHUCKLES ]

19:53.628 --> 19:57.565
FAST CARS, RODENT RAPE,
SUMMERS OFF ‐‐

19:57.598 --> 19:59.433
WOW, TO BE <i>YOU.</i>

19:59.467 --> 20:02.436
YOU THINK LIFE IS YOUR OWN
PRIVATE LITTLE JOKE,

20:02.470 --> 20:03.604
DON'T YOU, BOTWIN?

20:03.638 --> 20:06.140
YOU KNOW WHO ELSE
USED TO THINK THAT?

20:06.173 --> 20:07.241
YOUR PARENTS...

20:07.275 --> 20:09.944
BEFORE YOU SHOWED UP
AND SHIT ALL OVER THEIR DREAMS.

20:09.977 --> 20:12.480
NAH, NOTHING SHITS
ON MY MOM'S DREAMS,

20:12.513 --> 20:13.614
LEAST OF ALL ME.

20:13.648 --> 20:15.816
AND MY DAD'S DEAD.
BUT NICE TRY.

20:15.850 --> 20:17.985
GET IN,
WE'LL SETTLE UP,

20:18.019 --> 20:19.787
AND I'LL GIVE YOU
A RIDE HOME.

20:23.524 --> 20:25.293
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

20:25.326 --> 20:27.428
WOW, TO BE YOU!

20:27.461 --> 20:28.929
[ TIRES SQUEALING ]

20:30.865 --> 20:33.234
WHY CAN'T YOU
JUST WALK AWAY?

20:33.267 --> 20:35.770
WHY CAN'T YOU GO HOME,
FORGET ABOUT ALL THIS?

20:35.803 --> 20:38.873
NOTHING TO GO HOME TO.

20:38.906 --> 20:41.642
NOTHING AND NO ONE.

20:41.676 --> 20:43.744
NOT ANYMORE.

20:43.778 --> 20:45.379
[ SIGHS ]

20:45.413 --> 20:46.213
I KNOW IT'S SOON,

20:46.247 --> 20:48.082
BUT HAVE YOU THOUGHT
ABOUT DATING?

20:48.115 --> 20:50.284
HE WOULDN'T BE
WHO YOU HAD,

20:50.318 --> 20:52.586
BUT THERE'S SOMEONE ELSE
OUT THERE FOR YOU.

20:52.620 --> 20:56.057
MY UGLY COUSIN PAULO ‐‐

20:56.090 --> 20:58.993
HE MADE HIMSELF A FUCK DOLL
FROM A TIRE.

20:59.026 --> 21:01.062
<i>SOMEONE</i> OR <i>SOMETHING.</i>

21:01.095 --> 21:04.966
YOU HAVE TO CHOOSE, NANCY.
WHO'S IT GONNA BE?

21:04.999 --> 21:06.567
NO. I LET HIM GO,
HE KILLS YOU.

21:06.600 --> 21:07.735
I LET YOU GO,
YOU KILL HIM.

21:07.768 --> 21:08.769
I CAN'T HAVE THAT!

21:08.803 --> 21:11.038
COME ON, MOMMY.
PICK YOUR FAVORITE.

21:11.072 --> 21:13.407
'CAUSE YOU'RE RIGHT ‐‐
I'LL KILL HIM.

21:13.441 --> 21:15.176
IT'S WHAT I'M LIVING FOR.

21:15.209 --> 21:16.777
SEE, I TELL YOU.

21:16.811 --> 21:18.813
OR HE'LL KILL ME
WITHOUT BLINKING AN EYE

21:18.846 --> 21:19.880
AND THEN STUFF HIS FACE

21:19.914 --> 21:21.682
AND WATCH MOVIES
LIKE NOTHING HAPPENED.

21:21.716 --> 21:22.717
THAT'S TRUE, TOO.

21:22.750 --> 21:24.285
CHOOSE!
I CAN'T.

21:24.318 --> 21:26.354
I'M BRINGING A CHILD
INTO THE WORLD.

21:26.387 --> 21:29.123
[ SIGHS ]

21:29.156 --> 21:32.059
I'M NOT READY TO SIT HERE
AND PLAY BUDDHA

21:32.093 --> 21:35.363
AND BE FUCKING ZEN
ABOUT WHO LIVES OR DIES!

21:37.932 --> 21:40.968
SO WE WILL ASK THE MAGIC BALL.

21:42.336 --> 21:45.706
TELL ME, MAGIC BALL,

21:45.740 --> 21:48.476
CAN THESE TWO MEN PART IN PEACE

21:48.509 --> 21:50.478
AND LIVE TO KILL ANOTHER DAY?

21:50.511 --> 21:52.980
GO ON AND SHAKE
YOUR MAGIC BALL.

21:53.014 --> 21:54.715
TELL YOURSELF
YOU'RE SO NOBLE

21:54.749 --> 21:57.318
BECAUSE WE'RE BOTH
STILL BREATHING.

21:58.719 --> 22:01.222
YOU'VE GOT BLOOD
ON YOUR HANDS.

22:03.824 --> 22:06.127
JUST SIGN HERE AND HERE.

22:06.160 --> 22:09.130
MONTH TO MONTH.
THREE MONTHS DOWN.

22:09.163 --> 22:11.265
WELL, NOW, I WAS THINKING
12‐MONTH LEASE

22:11.299 --> 22:12.333
WITH 2 MONTHS DOWN.

22:14.135 --> 22:15.102
FINE.

22:15.136 --> 22:17.271
I'M REALLY GLAD
YOU CHANGED YOUR MIND.

22:17.305 --> 22:19.573
HE BEAT UP MY CAT.

22:19.607 --> 22:21.409
I LIKE YOUR STYLE.

22:21.442 --> 22:22.777
YEAH.

22:22.810 --> 22:24.211
JUST SIGN THE FUCKING PAPER
ALREADY.

22:26.647 --> 22:29.450
HMM.
WE'RE IN BUSINESS, <i>PARTNER.</i>

22:29.483 --> 22:30.985
PARTNER.
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:31.018 --> 22:33.454
PARTNERS.
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:33.487 --> 22:34.388
FAGGOTS.

22:35.723 --> 22:37.124
[ BIRDS CALLING ]

22:37.158 --> 22:39.994
HE WAS MY FIRST ‐‐
MY FIRST BOYFRIEND,

22:40.027 --> 22:42.797
MY FIRST LOVE,
AND MY FIRST...

22:42.830 --> 22:44.165
YOU KNOW.

22:44.198 --> 22:48.035
THEN HE WENT AWAY, AND MY LIFE
BECAME A BUCKET OF SHIT.

22:48.069 --> 22:49.737
WELL, I FEEL YOUR BUCKET.

22:49.770 --> 22:53.374
THAT WAS PRETTY SMART,
PRETENDING TO BE JUDAH.

22:53.407 --> 22:55.743
STATE TAXES, PROBATE
DRAIN THE WHOLE ACCOUNT.

22:55.776 --> 22:57.244
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:57.278 --> 22:59.614
WELL...

22:59.647 --> 23:01.682
MAYBE YOU COULD
HELP ME OUT.

23:01.716 --> 23:04.919
OH. I DON'T KNOW.
I COULD GET FIRED.

23:04.952 --> 23:07.888
OF COURSE,
THE BANK IS CLOSING ANYWAY.

23:07.922 --> 23:11.258
DOWNSIZING, RECESSION.
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:11.292 --> 23:14.695
YOU SORTA LOOK LIKE HIM.

23:14.729 --> 23:18.265
YOU HAVE THE SAME
KIND EYES.

23:19.467 --> 23:21.435
TELL ME MORE
ABOUT MY EYES.

23:24.372 --> 23:25.573
[ SIGHS ]

23:25.606 --> 23:27.675
ALL RIGHT,
HERE'S THE DEAL.

23:27.708 --> 23:29.043
YOU GO OUT WITH ME,

23:29.076 --> 23:31.112
AND I'LL GET YOU
INTO THAT ACCOUNT.

23:31.145 --> 23:33.748
I WAS GONNA
ASK YOU OUT ANYWAY.

23:33.781 --> 23:37.351
ONLY IT HAS TO BE AS JUDAH.
YOU'RE JUDAH, AND I'M ME.

23:37.385 --> 23:40.888
AND YOU HAVE TO LOVE ME
AND TREAT ME NICE.

23:42.156 --> 23:44.425
WELL, THERE'S NOTHING WEIRD
ABOUT <i>THAT.</i>

23:44.458 --> 23:47.461
UH, YEAH.
SURE, MARGARET.

23:47.495 --> 23:48.896
WHATEVER YOU SAY.

23:48.929 --> 23:52.333
MAGS.
JUDAH CALLS ME MAGS.

23:52.366 --> 23:54.802
[ LAUGHS ]

24:08.849 --> 24:10.685
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

24:10.718 --> 24:14.855
AS I SEE IT, YES.

24:14.889 --> 24:16.557
IT IS CERTAIN.

24:16.590 --> 24:18.726
IT IS DECIDEDLY SO.

24:18.759 --> 24:20.261
MOST LIKELY.

24:20.294 --> 24:21.896
OUTLOOK GOOD.

24:21.929 --> 24:24.265
SIGNS POINT TO YES.

24:24.298 --> 24:25.299
WITHOUT A DOUBT.

24:25.333 --> 24:26.867
REPLY HAZY, TRY AGAIN.

24:26.901 --> 24:29.737
ASK AGAIN LATER.
BETTER NOT TELL YOU NOW.

24:29.770 --> 24:31.405
CANNOT PREDICT NOW.

24:31.439 --> 24:33.207
DON'T COUNT ON IT.

24:33.240 --> 24:34.375
MY REPLY IS NO.

24:34.408 --> 24:36.377
MY SOURCES SAY NO.

24:36.410 --> 24:39.547
OUTLOOK NOT SO GOOD.

24:39.580 --> 24:42.316
VERY DOUBTFUL.

24:45.286 --> 24:47.188
[ SIGHS ]

24:47.221 --> 24:49.824
SO, "NO."

24:49.857 --> 24:51.359
NOT ALL RIGHT.

25:07.241 --> 25:09.277
WHAT'S GOING TO HAPPEN
IN THERE...

25:11.312 --> 25:13.347
...IS NOT RIGHT OR WRONG.

25:13.381 --> 25:15.116
IT'S NOT GOOD OR BAD.

25:15.149 --> 25:17.285
IT <i>IS.</i>

25:22.523 --> 25:25.760
IT'S WHAT HAPPENS NEXT.

25:27.528 --> 25:30.164
WE CHOSE.

25:30.197 --> 25:32.033
YOU AND I.

25:32.066 --> 25:36.304
WHEN WE CAME TOGETHER,
WE CHOSE...

25:36.337 --> 25:39.073
A LIFE, THIS LIFE,

25:39.106 --> 25:42.109
FOR YOU, FOR ME,
FOR OUR SON.

25:42.143 --> 25:46.681
AND THERE IS NOTHING
I WILL NOT DO

25:46.714 --> 25:49.216
TO PROTECT THAT LIFE.

26:22.350 --> 26:24.385
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

27:34.588 --> 27:37.792
